<pre><code class="lang-auto">    @Override
    public boolean runsWhenDisabled()
    {
        return true;
    }
</code></pre>
<p>and then for example a command that updates some LED pattern will run just fine while disabled.<br>
You can for example schedule it in <code>disabledInit()</code>.</p>
